Mercantile Bank Surges to Highest in 13 Months After Bidvest Takeover Bid

-- B y   A n a   M o n t e i r o
-- 
2011-07-01T07:06:27Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-01/mercantile-bank-surges-to-highest-in-13-months-after-bidvest-takeover-bid.html
  Mercantile Bank Holdings Ltd. (MTL) , a
South African lender, surged to the highest intraday level in 13
months after receiving an unsolicited takeover offer from
 Bidvest Group Ltd. (BVT)   The stock soared for a second day, adding 4 cents, or 16
percent, to 29 cents by 9:03 a.m. in Johannesburg, the strongest
intraday price since May 2010.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ana Monteiro at 
 amonteiro4@bloomberg.net  